rows.label: qev055404_MSG0001
rows.name:
The will Kun'luarb passed on to you remains strong and
clear within me as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055404_MSG0002
rows.name: I hope you will see through on the promise you made.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055404_MSG0003
rows.name:
Senirapa water is a scarce resource on Mira, but if you
scour the land, I am certain you will find more in time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055404_MSG0004
rows.name:
Just as Kun'luarb searched before you,
most tireless in his dedication...[ST:wait ]
